snippet.title: Mortal Kombat 4 NES Bootleg Playthrough
snippet.description:
i played this many years ago, so i decided to play through it again on the RetroAVS

this is the more common version of the bootleg were it removes Kano Sub-Zero, Nightwolf (he becomes Blue Shao Khan)
